Pemex says two crude ports shut due to bad weather . Petroleos Mexicanos said two crude oil shipping ports were closed at 7 a . m . ( 1300 GMT ) because of high winds . The state - owned oil and gas company said Dos Bocas in Tabasco state and Pajaritos in Veracruz state along the Gulf of Mexico were shut . The two terminals are among Pemex ' s three main crude exporting sites . - - Timna Tanners , Mexico City newsroom + 525 728 7903 
